(2989, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2989/the-big-bang-theory-4x14-the-thespian-catalyst', 'The Thespian Catalyst', 4, 14, 'regular', '2011-02-03', '20:00', '2011-02-04T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12334.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12334.jpg', '<p>Sheldon hopes acting lessons from Penny will help him become a better teacher. Meanwhile, Koothrappali fantasizes about his best friend\'s girlfriend.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2989'),
(2990, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2990/the-big-bang-theory-4x15-the-benefactor-factor', 'The Benefactor Factor', 4, 15, 'regular', '2011-02-10', '20:00', '2011-02-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12335.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12335.jpg', '<p>A wealthy donor to the university makes Leonard consider how far he\'s willing to go for the sake of science.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2990'),
(2991, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2991/the-big-bang-theory-4x16-the-cohabitation-formulation', 'The Cohabitation Formulation', 4, 16, 'regular', '2011-02-17', '20:00', '2011-02-18T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12336.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12336.jpg', '<p>As Wolowitz contemplates taking things with Bernadette to the next level, Leonard rekindles his relationship with Raj\'s sister.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2991'),
(2992, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2992/the-big-bang-theory-4x17-the-toast-derivation', 'The Toast Derivation', 4, 17, 'regular', '2011-02-24', '20:00', '2011-02-25T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12337.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12337.jpg', '<p>Sheldon struggles to cope when he realizes it\'s actually Leonard who is the center of their social group.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2992'),
(2993, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2993/the-big-bang-theory-4x18-the-prestidigitation-approximation', 'The Prestidigitation Approximation', 4, 18, 'regular', '2011-03-10', '20:00', '2011-03-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12338.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12338.jpg', '<p>Leonard must choose between new girlfriend Priya and his friendship with Penny. Meanwhile, Howard drives Sheldon crazy with a magic trick.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2993'),
(2994, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2994/the-big-bang-theory-4x19-the-zarnecki-incursion', 'The Zarnecki Incursion', 4, 19, 'regular', '2011-03-31', '20:00', '2011-04-01T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12339.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12339.jpg', '<p>When someone hacks Sheldon\'s online game account, the guys go on a quest to find the culprit.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2994'),
(2995, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2995/the-big-bang-theory-4x20-the-herb-garden-germination', 'The Herb Garden Germination', 4, 20, 'regular', '2011-04-07', '20:00', '2011-04-08T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12340.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12340.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy experiment on their friends by spreading gossip, while Howard takes a big step in his relationship with Bernadette.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2995'),
(2996, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2996/the-big-bang-theory-4x21-the-agreement-dissection', 'The Agreement Dissection', 4, 21, 'regular', '2011-04-28', '20:00', '2011-04-29T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12341.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12341.jpg', '<p>When Priya uses her lawyer skills to pick apart the roommate agreement, the girls take Sheldon dancing.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2996'),
(2997, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2997/the-big-bang-theory-4x22-the-wildebeest-implementation', 'The Wildebeest Implementation', 4, 22, 'regular', '2011-05-05', '20:00', '2011-05-06T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12342.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12342.jpg', '<p>Raj attempts to cure his social anxiety disorder while Penny uses Bernadette to spy on Leonard and his girlfriend.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2997'),
(2998, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2998/the-big-bang-theory-4x23-the-engagement-reaction', 'The Engagement Reaction', 4, 23, 'regular', '2011-05-12', '20:00', '2011-05-13T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12343.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12343.jpg', '<p>When Howard finally breaks the news to his mom that he\'s engaged to Bernadette, it lands her in the hospital.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2998'),
(2999, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2999/the-big-bang-theory-4x24-the-roommate-transmogrification', 'The Roommate Transmogrification', 4, 24, 'regular', '2011-05-19', '20:00', '2011-05-20T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12344.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12344.jpg', '<p>When Bernadette receives her Ph.D., the guys take joy in reminding an emasculated Wolowitz that he is the only one in their group who isn\'t a doctor. Meanwhile, Koothrappali becomes Sheldon\'s new roommate after hearing Leonard and Priya engaging in a \"Star Trek\" bedroom fantasy.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/2999'),
(3000, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3000/the-big-bang-theory-5x01-the-skank-reflex-analysis', 'The Skank Reflex Analysis', 5, 1, 'regular', '2011-09-22', '20:00', '2011-09-23T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12266.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12266.jpg', '<p>Penny worries that she\'s screwed things up permanently with her friends, while Sheldon takes command of the paintball team.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3000'),
(3001, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3001/the-big-bang-theory-5x02-the-infestation-hypothesis', 'The Infestation Hypothesis', 5, 2, 'regular', '2011-09-22', '20:30', '2011-09-23T00:30:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12267.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12267.jpg', '<p>Fight between Sheldon and Penny leaves Amy caught in the middle, while Leonard tries to spice up his long-distance relationship with Priya.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3001'),
(3002, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3002/the-big-bang-theory-5x03-the-pulled-groin-extrapolation', 'The Pulled Groin Extrapolation', 5, 3, 'regular', '2011-09-29', '20:00', '2011-09-30T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12268.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12268.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Amy get to know each other better, while Howard and Bernadette spend the weekend with Mrs. Wolowitz.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3002'),
(3003, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3003/the-big-bang-theory-5x04-the-wiggly-finger-catalyst', 'The Wiggly Finger Catalyst', 5, 4, 'regular', '2011-10-06', '20:00', '2011-10-07T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12269.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12269.jpg', '<p>Raj finally meets a girl he can communicate with.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3003'),
(3004, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3004/the-big-bang-theory-5x05-the-russian-rocket-reaction', 'The Russian Rocket Reaction', 5, 5, 'regular', '2011-10-13', '20:00', '2011-10-14T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12270.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12270.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Leonard get invited to a party at Wil Wheaton\'s house, and Howard gets an out-of-this-world opportunity.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3004'),
(3005, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3005/the-big-bang-theory-5x06-the-rhinitis-revelation', 'The Rhinitis Revelation', 5, 6, 'regular', '2011-10-20', '20:00', '2011-10-21T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12271.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12271.jpg', '<p>Sheldon competes with the gang for his mother\'s attention when she comes to visit.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3005'),
(3006, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3006/the-big-bang-theory-5x07-the-good-guy-fluctuation', 'The Good Guy Fluctuation', 5, 7, 'regular', '2011-10-27', '20:00', '2011-10-28T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12272.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12272.jpg', '<p>Cute comic book artist puts Leonard and Priya\'s relationship to the test, while Sheldon tries to scare the guys for Halloween.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3006');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `url`, `name`, `season`, `number`, `type`, `airdate`, `airtime`, `airstamp`, `runtime`, `imagemedium`, `imageoriginal`, `summary`, `linksselfhref`) VALUES
(3007, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3007/the-big-bang-theory-5x08-the-isolation-permutation', 'The Isolation Permutation', 5, 8, 'regular', '2011-11-03', '20:00', '2011-11-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12273.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12273.jpg', '<p>Amy is crushed when Bernadette and Penny go shopping for wedding dresses without her.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3007'),
(3008, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3008/the-big-bang-theory-5x09-the-ornithophobia-diffusion', 'The Ornithophobia Diffusion', 5, 9, 'regular', '2011-11-10', '20:00', '2011-11-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12274.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12274.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Penny try hanging out alone, and Sheldon must overcome his fear of birds.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3008'),
(3009, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3009/the-big-bang-theory-5x10-the-flaming-spittoon-acquisition', 'The Flaming Spittoon Acquisition', 5, 10, 'regular', '2011-11-17', '20:00', '2011-11-18T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12275.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12275.jpg', '<p>Sheldon considers taking his relationship with Amy to the next level when Stuart from the comic book store asks her out on a date.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3009'),
(3010, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3010/the-big-bang-theory-5x11-the-speckerman-recurrence', 'The Speckerman Recurrence', 5, 11, 'regular', '2011-12-08', '20:00', '2011-12-09T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12276.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12276.jpg', '<p>Leonard must face his fears after being contacted by his high school tormentor.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3010'),
(3011, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3011/the-big-bang-theory-5x12-the-shiny-trinket-maneuver', 'The Shiny Trinket Maneuver', 5, 12, 'regular', '2012-01-12', '20:00', '2012-01-13T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12277.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12277.jpg', '<p>Sheldon gets in trouble with Amy when he isn\'t impressed by her recent accomplishment, and Howard must come to grips with Bernadette\'s dislike of children.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3011'),
(3012, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3012/the-big-bang-theory-5x13-the-recombination-hypothesis', 'The Recombination Hypothesis', 5, 13, 'regular', '2012-01-19', '20:00', '2012-01-20T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12278.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12278.jpg', '<p>Everything might change when Leonard offers Penny a spur of the moment invitation to a romantic dinner for two.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3012'),
(3013, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3013/the-big-bang-theory-5x14-the-beta-test-initiation', 'The Beta Test Initiation', 5, 14, 'regular', '2012-01-26', '20:00', '2012-01-27T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12279.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12279.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Penny experiment with dating, while Raj develops a peculiar relationship with his phone\'s virtual assistant.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3013'),
(3014, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3014/the-big-bang-theory-5x15-the-friendship-contraction', 'The Friendship Contraction', 5, 15, 'regular', '2012-02-02', '20:00', '2012-02-03T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12280.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12280.jpg', '<p>Sheldon\'s selfish demands force Leonard to reconsider their friendship. Meanwhile, Wolowitz tries to pick his astronaut nickname.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3014'),
(3015, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3015/the-big-bang-theory-5x16-the-vacation-solution', 'The Vacation Solution', 5, 16, 'regular', '2012-02-09', '20:00', '2012-02-10T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12293.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12293.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon is forced to take his vacation, he goes to work with Amy in her neurobiology lab. Meanwhile, Bernadette wants Howard to sign a pre-nup.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3015'),
(3016, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3016/the-big-bang-theory-5x17-the-rothman-disintegration', 'The Rothman Disintegration', 5, 17, 'regular', '2012-02-16', '20:00', '2012-02-17T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12294.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12294.jpg', '<p>When an office at the University opens up, Sheldon must compete for it with his archenemy, Kripke. Meanwhile, a gift from Amy makes Penny uncomfortable.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3016'),
(3017, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3017/the-big-bang-theory-5x18-the-werewolf-transformation', 'The Werewolf Transformation', 5, 18, 'regular', '2012-02-23', '20:00', '2012-02-24T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12295.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12295.jpg', '<p>Sheldon\'s life is turned upside-down after his barber gets sick. Meanwhile, astronaut training causes Wolowitz to rethink his decision to go into space.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3017'),
(3018, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3018/the-big-bang-theory-5x19-the-weekend-vortex', 'The Weekend Vortex', 5, 19, 'regular', '2012-03-08', '20:00', '2012-03-09T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12297.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12297.jpg', '<p>Sheldon chooses to play video games with the guys rather than go with Amy to her aunt\'s birthday party.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3018'),
(3019, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3019/the-big-bang-theory-5x20-the-transporter-malfunction', 'The Transporter Malfunction', 5, 20, 'regular', '2012-03-29', '20:00', '2012-03-30T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12298.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12298.jpg', '<p>Penny buys Leonard and Sheldon \"Star Trek\" collectibles as a thank-you, leading Sheldon to be haunted by Mr. Spock. Meanwhile, Raj decides he has met the \"Future Mrs. Koothrappali\" after his parents set him up on a date.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3019'),
(3020, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3020/the-big-bang-theory-5x21-the-hawking-excitation', 'The Hawking Excitation', 5, 21, 'regular', '2012-04-05', '20:00', '2012-04-06T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12299.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12299.jpg', '<p>When Wolowitz gets to work with Stephen Hawking, Sheldon is willing to do anything to meet his hero.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3020'),
(3021, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3021/the-big-bang-theory-5x22-the-stag-convergence', 'The Stag Convergence', 5, 22, 'regular', '2012-04-26', '20:00', '2012-04-27T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12301.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12301.jpg', '<p>Bernadette reconsiders marrying Howard after learning about his sexual history.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3021'),
(3022, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3022/the-big-bang-theory-5x23-the-launch-acceleration', 'The Launch Acceleration', 5, 23, 'regular', '2012-05-03', '20:00', '2012-05-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12302.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12302.jpg', '<p>NASA reschedules Howard\'s mission, putting his and Bernadette\'s wedding plans in jeopardy. Meanwhile, Leonard says something surprising to Penny in the bedroom.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3022'),
(3023, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3023/the-big-bang-theory-5x24-the-countdown-reflection', 'The Countdown Reflection', 5, 24, 'regular', '2012-05-10', '20:00', '2012-05-11T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12303.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12303.jpg', '<p>When Howard and Bernadette decide they want to be married before his NASA launch, the gang rushes to put on a wedding.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3023'),
(3024, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3024/the-big-bang-theory-6x01-the-date-night-variable', 'The Date Night Variable', 6, 1, 'regular', '2012-09-27', '20:00', '2012-09-28T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12507.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12507.jpg', '<p>With his friends on dates, Raj must face his loneliness. Also, Wolowitz is caught in an argument between Bernadette and his mom, even while he\'s in space.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3024'),
(3025, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3025/the-big-bang-theory-6x02-the-decoupling-fluctuation', 'The Decoupling Fluctuation', 6, 2, 'regular', '2012-10-04', '20:00', '2012-10-05T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12508.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12508.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon learns that Penny is thinking about breaking up with Leonard, he tries to intervene. Meanwhile, in space, the other astronauts pick on Howard.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3025'),
(3026, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3026/the-big-bang-theory-6x03-the-higgs-boson-observation', 'The Higgs Boson Observation', 6, 3, 'regular', '2012-10-11', '20:00', '2012-10-12T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12509.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12509.jpg', '<p>Amy feels threatened when Sheldon hires a young female assistant, and the pressure of being in space takes its toll on Wolowitz.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3026'),
(3027, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3027/the-big-bang-theory-6x04-the-re-entry-minimization', 'The Re-Entry Minimization', 6, 4, 'regular', '2012-10-18', '20:00', '2012-10-19T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12510.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12510.jpg', '<p>When Wolowitz returns from space, he doesn\'t get the hero\'s welcome he expected. Meanwhile, Game Night turns into a battle of the sexes.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3027'),
(3028, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3028/the-big-bang-theory-6x05-the-holographic-excitation', 'The Holographic Excitation', 6, 5, 'regular', '2012-10-25', '20:00', '2012-10-26T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12511.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12511.jpg', '<p>The gang celebrates Halloween at Stuart\'s comic book store. Meanwhile, Leonard seduces Penny with science.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3028'),
(3029, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3029/the-big-bang-theory-6x06-the-extract-obliteration', 'The Extract Obliteration', 6, 6, 'regular', '2012-11-01', '20:00', '2012-11-02T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12512.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12512.jpg', '<p>Sheldon\'s relationship with Stephen Hawking is threatened over a game of \"Words with Friends,\" and Penny secretly enrolls in a class at the local college.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3029'),
(3030, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3030/the-big-bang-theory-6x07-the-habitation-configuration', 'The Habitation Configuration', 6, 7, 'regular', '2012-11-08', '20:00', '2012-11-09T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12489.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12489.jpg', '<p>Wolowitz struggles with moving out of his mother\'s house. Meanwhile, Sheldon is caught in the middle of an argument between Amy and Wil Wheaton.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3030'),
(3031, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3031/the-big-bang-theory-6x08-the-43-peculiarity', 'The 43 Peculiarity', 6, 8, 'regular', '2012-11-15', '20:00', '2012-11-16T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12490.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12490.jpg', '<p>Howard and Raj try to get to the bottom of why Sheldon disappears every afternoon at 2:45. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny deal with jealousy in their relationship.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3031'),
(3032, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3032/the-big-bang-theory-6x09-the-parking-spot-escalation', 'The Parking Spot Escalation', 6, 9, 'regular', '2012-11-29', '20:00', '2012-11-30T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12491.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12491.jpg', '<p>When the University reassigns Sheldon\'s parking spot to Wolowitz, their fight affects the whole gang.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3032'),
(3033, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3033/the-big-bang-theory-6x10-the-fish-guts-displacement', 'The Fish Guts Displacement', 6, 10, 'regular', '2012-12-06', '20:00', '2012-12-07T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12492.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12492.jpg', '<p>Sheldon tries to nurse a sick Amy back to health, while Wolowitz prepares for an upcoming fishing trip with his father-in-law.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3033'),
(3034, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3034/the-big-bang-theory-6x11-the-santa-simulation', 'The Santa Simulation', 6, 11, 'regular', '2012-12-13', '20:00', '2012-12-14T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12493.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12493.jpg', '<p>Sheldon revisits some Christmas memories during a game of Dungeons and Dragons, while Penny, Bernadette and Amy try to find a girl for Koothrappali when he joins the girls for ladies\' night.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3034'),
(3035, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3035/the-big-bang-theory-6x12-the-egg-salad-equivalency', 'The Egg Salad Equivalency', 6, 12, 'regular', '2013-01-03', '20:00', '2013-01-04T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12494.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12494.jpg', '<p>Sheldon gets accused of sexual harassment at the University and winds up getting Leonard, Raj and Wolowitz in trouble.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3035'),
(3036, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3036/the-big-bang-theory-6x13-the-bakersfield-expedition', 'The Bakersfield Expedition', 6, 13, 'regular', '2013-01-10', '20:00', '2013-01-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12495.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12495.jpg', '<p>While the guys take a road trip to a comic book convention dressed as \"Star Trek: The Next Generation\" characters, the girls stay home and try to interpret a comic book.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3036'),
(3037, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3037/the-big-bang-theory-6x14-the-cooperkripke-inversion', 'The Cooper/Kripke Inversion', 6, 14, 'regular', '2013-01-31', '20:00', '2013-02-01T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12496.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12496.jpg', '<p>Sheldon is forced to work with Barry Kripke and faces a crisis of confidence. Meanwhile, Howard and Raj spend $1,000 on action figures of themselves.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3037'),
(3038, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3038/the-big-bang-theory-6x15-the-spoiler-alert-segmentation', 'The Spoiler Alert Segmentation', 6, 15, 'regular', '2013-02-07', '20:00', '2013-02-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12497.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12497.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon and Leonard fight, it affects Penny and Amy\'s living arrangements. Meanwhile, Raj takes care of Mrs. Wolowitz while Howard is away.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3038'),
(3039, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3039/the-big-bang-theory-6x16-the-tangible-affection-proof', 'The Tangible Affection Proof', 6, 16, 'regular', '2013-02-14', '20:00', '2013-02-15T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12498.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12498.jpg', '<p>While the guys try to give their significant others the perfect Valentine\'s Day, Raj and Stuart throw a \"lonely people\" party at the comic book store.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3039'),
(3040, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3040/the-big-bang-theory-6x17-the-monster-isolation', 'The Monster Isolation', 6, 17, 'regular', '2013-02-21', '20:00', '2013-02-22T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12499.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12499.jpg', '<p>After a terrible date, Koothrappali vows to never leave his apartment. Meanwhile, Penny actually impresses Sheldon with her acting skills.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3040'),
(3041, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3041/the-big-bang-theory-6x18-the-contractual-obligation-implementation', 'The Contractual Obligation Implementation', 6, 18, 'regular', '2013-03-07', '20:00', '2013-03-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12500.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12500.jpg', '<p>Leonard, Sheldon and Wolowitz speak to junior high girls about careers in science. Meanwhile, Koothrappali plans a date with Lucy.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3041'),
(3042, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3042/the-big-bang-theory-6x19-the-closet-reconfiguration', 'The Closet Reconfiguration', 6, 19, 'regular', '2013-03-14', '20:00', '2013-03-15T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12501.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12501.jpg', '<p>Howard struggles with whether or not he should open a letter from his father, and Leonard and Penny throw a \"grown-up\" cocktail party at the apartment.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3042'),
(3043, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3043/the-big-bang-theory-6x20-the-tenure-turbulence', 'The Tenure Turbulence', 6, 20, 'regular', '2013-04-04', '20:00', '2013-04-05T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12502.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12502.jpg', '<p>Leonard, Sheldon and Raj fight for tenure at the University, and the competition heats up when the girls get involved.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3043'),
(3044, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3044/the-big-bang-theory-6x21-the-closure-alternative', 'The Closure Alternative', 6, 21, 'regular', '2013-04-25', '20:00', '2013-04-26T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12503.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12503.jpg', '<p>Sheldon feels lost after one of his favorite TV shows gets canceled too soon and Amy tries to help him get over his compulsive need for closure. Meanwhile, Raj discovers a secret about his new love interest, Lucy.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3044'),
(3045, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3045/the-big-bang-theory-6x22-the-proton-resurgence', 'The Proton Resurgence', 6, 22, 'regular', '2013-05-02', '20:00', '2013-05-03T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12504.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12504.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Leonard hire Professor Proton, the host of their favorite childhood TV show, to perform. Also, Howard and Bernadette run into trouble babysitting Raj\'s dog.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3045'),
(3046, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3046/the-big-bang-theory-6x23-the-love-spell-potential', 'The Love Spell Potential', 6, 23, 'regular', '2013-05-09', '20:00', '2013-05-10T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12505.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12505.jpg', '<p>When the girls\' trip to Vegas falls through, the guys invite them to play Dungeons &amp; Dragons, causing Sheldon and Amy\'s relationship to take an unexpected turn. Meanwhile, Koothrappali and Lucy go on a very awkward date.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3046'),
(3047, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3047/the-big-bang-theory-6x24-the-bon-voyage-reaction', 'The Bon Voyage Reaction', 6, 24, 'regular', '2013-05-16', '20:00', '2013-05-17T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/12506.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/12506.jpg', '<p>New success for Leonard makes Sheldon very jealous and throws Penny for a loop. Meanwhile, Koothrappali pushes Lucy too far in their relationship.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3047'),
(3048, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3048/the-big-bang-theory-7x01-the-hofstadter-insufficiency', 'The Hofstadter Insufficiency', 7, 1, 'regular', '2013-09-26', '20:00', '2013-09-27T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12100.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12100.jpg', '<p>With Leonard away, Sheldon and Penny spend quality time together sharing intimate secrets. Also, Wolowitz helps Raj get over his ex-girlfriend.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3048'),
(3049, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3049/the-big-bang-theory-7x02-the-deception-verification', 'The Deception Verification', 7, 2, 'regular', '2013-09-26', '20:31', '2013-09-27T00:31:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12101.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12101.jpg', '<p>Leonard\'s friendship with Sheldon is put to the test when he returns from the North Sea. Meanwhile, Wolowitz\'s relationship with his mother causes an unusual threat to his masculinity.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3049'),
(3050, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3050/the-big-bang-theory-7x03-the-scavenger-vortex', 'The Scavenger Vortex', 7, 3, 'regular', '2013-10-03', '20:00', '2013-10-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12102.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12102.jpg', '<p>When the entire gang competes in a scavenger hunt designed by Raj, it brings out the best - and worst - in everyone.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3050'),
(3051, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3051/the-big-bang-theory-7x04-the-raiders-minimization', 'The Raiders Minimization', 7, 4, 'regular', '2013-10-10', '20:00', '2013-10-11T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12103.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12103.jpg', '<p>Sheldon seeks revenge after Amy ruins one of his favorite movies. Meanwhile, Leonard discovers a way to get Penny to do anything, and Raj and Stuart create online dating profiles.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3051'),
(3052, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3052/the-big-bang-theory-7x05-the-workplace-proximity', 'The Workplace Proximity', 7, 5, 'regular', '2013-10-17', '20:00', '2013-10-18T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12104.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12104.jpg', '<p>Sheldon must decide how much \"Amy time\" is too much after she takes a job at his university. Meanwhile, Howard finds himself sleeping on Raj\'s couch after a fight with Bernadette.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3052'),
(3053, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3053/the-big-bang-theory-7x06-the-romance-resonance', 'The Romance Resonance', 7, 6, 'regular', '2013-10-24', '20:00', '2013-10-25T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12105.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12105.jpg', '<p>Sheldon\'s major scientific breakthrough makes him feel like a fraud. Meanwhile, Howard\'s romantic gesture to Bernadette causes Penny to step up her game with Leonard.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3053'),
(3054, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3054/the-big-bang-theory-7x07-the-proton-displacement', 'The Proton Displacement', 7, 7, 'regular', '2013-11-07', '20:00', '2013-11-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12106.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12106.jpg', '<p>Sheldon feels slighted when Professor Proton seeks advice from Leonard instead of him, and he seeks revenge by befriending a rival science TV host, Bill Nye. Meanwhile, Raj gets jealous when Howard crashes \"girls\' night\".</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3054'),
(3055, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3055/the-big-bang-theory-7x08-the-itchy-brain-simulation', 'The Itchy Brain Simulation', 7, 8, 'regular', '2013-11-14', '20:00', '2013-11-15T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12107.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12107.jpg', '<p>Leonard tries to keep Sheldon from overreacting when a past mistake comes to light, but Sheldon punishes Leonard by making him walk a mile in his shoes. Meanwhile, Penny confronts Raj\'s ex-girlfriend, Lucy.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3055'),
(3056, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3056/the-big-bang-theory-7x09-the-thanksgiving-decoupling', 'The Thanksgiving Decoupling', 7, 9, 'regular', '2013-11-21', '20:00', '2013-11-22T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12108.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12108.jpg', '<p>Sheldon protests when the gang drags him to Mrs. Wolowitz\'s house for Thanksgiving. Meanwhile, Penny and Leonard must deal with a mistake from her past.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3056'),
(3057, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3057/the-big-bang-theory-7x10-the-discovery-dissipation', 'The Discovery Dissipation', 7, 10, 'regular', '2013-12-05', '20:00', '2013-12-06T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12109.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12109.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Amy help Sheldon cope with the shame he\'s feeling after his accidental contribution to science is disproved. Meanwhile, Raj must stay with Howard and Bernadette for a week.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3057'),
(3058, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3058/the-big-bang-theory-7x11-the-cooper-extraction', 'The Cooper Extraction', 7, 11, 'regular', '2013-12-12', '20:00', '2013-12-13T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12110.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12110.jpg', '<p>While Sheldon is away in Texas, everyone gathers to decorate the apartment Christmas tree, and they each realize how much he has changed their lives.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3058'),
(3059, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3059/the-big-bang-theory-7x12-the-hesitation-ramification', 'The Hesitation Ramification', 7, 12, 'regular', '2014-01-02', '20:00', '2014-01-03T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12111.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12111.jpg', '<p>When Penny\'s big acting break on NCIS is a bust, Leonard struggles to help her, which results in Penny asking Leonard a bold relationship question. Meanwhile, Sheldon tries to learn how to be funny and Raj tries to work on his \"game\" before talking to girls.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3059'),
(3060, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3060/the-big-bang-theory-7x13-the-occupation-recalibration', 'The Occupation Recalibration', 7, 13, 'regular', '2014-01-09', '20:00', '2014-01-10T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12112.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12112.jpg', '<p>Sheldon tries to relax after he is forced to take a vacation. Meanwhile, Leonard struggles to be supportive of Penny after she quits her job, and Bernadette seeks Stuart\'s help in replacing one of Howard\'s comic books.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3060'),
(3061, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3061/the-big-bang-theory-7x14-the-convention-conundrum', 'The Convention Conundrum', 7, 14, 'regular', '2014-01-30', '20:00', '2014-01-31T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12113.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12113.jpg', '<p>After the guys can\'t get Comic-Con tickets, Sheldon tries to hold his own convention and winds up spending a wild night with James Earl Jones. Meanwhile, the girls see if they can act like \"grown-ups\".</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3061'),
(3062, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3062/the-big-bang-theory-7x15-the-locomotive-manipulation', 'The Locomotive Manipulation', 7, 15, 'regular', '2014-02-06', '20:00', '2014-02-07T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12114.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12114.jpg', '<p>Love is in the air when Sheldon and Amy join Howard and Bernadette for a trip to wine country. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny must rush Raj\'s dog to the vet.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3062'),
(3063, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3063/the-big-bang-theory-7x16-the-table-polarization', 'The Table Polarization', 7, 16, 'regular', '2014-02-27', '20:00', '2014-02-28T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12115.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12115.jpg', '<p>Leonard buys a dining room table and it causes Sheldon to reevaluate the changes in his life. Meanwhile, Wolowitz is offered a chance to go back to space and Bernadette struggles with whether or not to encourage him.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3063'),
(3064, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3064/the-big-bang-theory-7x17-the-friendship-turbulence', 'The Friendship Turbulence', 7, 17, 'regular', '2014-03-06', '20:00', '2014-03-07T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12116.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12116.jpg', '<p>After the insults fly, Bernadette tries to broker the peace between Wolowitz and Sheldon. Meanwhile, Penny is offered an embarrassing movie role and Raj asks Amy to write to a woman on his behalf.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3064'),
(3065, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3065/the-big-bang-theory-7x18-the-mommy-observation', 'The Mommy Observation', 7, 18, 'regular', '2014-03-13', '20:00', '2014-03-14T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12117.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12117.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon visits his Mom in Houston, he is forced to confront a new reality. Meanwhile, Raj\'s \'Murder Mystery\' party starts some fights within the gang.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3065'),
(3066, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3066/the-big-bang-theory-7x19-the-indecision-amalgamation', 'The Indecision Amalgamation', 7, 19, 'regular', '2014-04-03', '20:00', '2014-04-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12118.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12118.jpg', '<p>While Raj is wracked with guilt when he tries to date two women at once, Penny wrestles with whether to take a role in a cheesy movie and Sheldon is torn trying to choose between two gaming systems.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3066'),
(3067, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3067/the-big-bang-theory-7x20-the-relationship-diremption', 'The Relationship Diremption', 7, 20, 'regular', '2014-04-10', '20:00', '2014-04-11T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12119.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12119.jpg', '<p>Sheldon faces a personal crisis after deciding he\'s wasting his time with string theory. Meanwhile, a double date between Raj, Emily and the Wolowitzes ends in embarrassment for Howard.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3067'),
(3068, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3068/the-big-bang-theory-7x21-the-anything-can-happen-recurrence', 'The Anything Can Happen Recurrence', 7, 21, 'regular', '2014-04-24', '20:00', '2014-04-25T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12120.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12120.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon tries to be spontaneous, it leads to unexpected friction between Penny, Amy and Bernadette. Meanwhile, Raj seeks Howard\'s help in preparing for a date with Emily.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3068'),
(3069, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3069/the-big-bang-theory-7x22-the-proton-transmogrification', 'The Proton Transmogrification', 7, 22, 'regular', '2014-05-01', '20:00', '2014-05-02T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12121.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12121.jpg', '<p>Professor Proton helps Sheldon cope with grief, while Leonard turns a relationship milestone into a competition with Penny. Meanwhile, Amy and Bernadette make a \"Star Wars Day\" gift for the guys.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3069'),
(3070, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3070/the-big-bang-theory-7x23-the-gorilla-dissolution', 'The Gorilla Dissolution', 7, 23, 'regular', '2014-05-08', '20:00', '2014-05-09T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12122.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12122.jpg', '<p>Bad day causes Penny to reevaluate her life choices - including Leonard. Meanwhile, Howard and Bernadette struggle to care for Mrs. Wolowitz, and Raj gets relationship advice from Sheldon.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3070'),
(3071, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3071/the-big-bang-theory-7x24-the-status-quo-combustion', 'The Status Quo Combustion', 7, 24, 'regular', '2014-05-15', '20:00', '2014-05-16T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/12123.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12123.jpg', '<p>Sheldon is forced to confront an uncertain future and considers a major move. Meanwhile, Raj and Emily take it to the next level, and Mrs. Wolowitz\'s injury is a major headache for Howard and Bernadette.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3071'),
(3072, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3072/the-big-bang-theory-8x01-the-locomotion-interruption', 'The Locomotion Interruption', 8, 1, 'regular', '2014-09-22', '20:00', '2014-09-23T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/1/4498.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/1/4498.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Amy take an unexpected road trip to Arizona to pick up Sheldon. Meanwhile, Penny interviews for a job at Bernadette\'s company, and Howard is weirded out by Stuart\'s relationship with Mrs. Wolowitz.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3072'),
(3073, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3073/the-big-bang-theory-8x02-the-junior-professor-solution', 'The Junior Professor Solution', 8, 2, 'regular', '2014-09-22', '20:00', '2014-09-23T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/1/4499.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/1/4499.jpg', '<p>Sheldon is ordered to teach a class, and the gang is surprised when Howard signs up to take it; and tensions between Penny and Bernadette afford Amy an opportunity to play one against the other.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3073'),
(3074, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3074/the-big-bang-theory-8x03-the-first-pitch-insufficiency', 'The First Pitch Insufficiency', 8, 3, 'regular', '2014-09-29', '20:00', '2014-09-30T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/1/4500.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/1/4500.jpg', '<p>Wolowitz is nervous after NASA asks him to throw out the first pitch at a Los Angeles Angels game. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny try to prove Sheldon wrong after he says that he and Amy are a \"superior couple\".</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3074'),
(7913, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/7913/the-big-bang-theory-8x04-the-hook-up-reverberation', 'The Hook-Up Reverberation', 8, 4, 'regular', '2014-10-06', '20:00', '2014-10-07T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/1/4501.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/1/4501.jpg', '<p>Raj\'s honesty about his past comes back to haunt him after his girlfriend, Emily, is cold to Penny. Also, the guys consider becoming part-owners in Stuart\'s comic book store.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/7913'),
(11229, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/11229/the-big-bang-theory-8x05-the-focus-attentuation', 'The Focus Attentuation', 8, 5, 'regular', '2014-10-13', '20:00', '2014-10-14T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/1/4502.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/1/4502.jpg', '<p>Amy and Bernadette accuse Penny of being a \"buzzkill\" after she gets an email from work during their Vegas weekend. Meanwhile, the guys try to invent something cool, but only come up with new ways to procrastinate.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/11229'),
(13149, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/13149/the-big-bang-theory-8x06-the-expedition-approximation', 'The Expedition Approximation', 8, 6, 'regular', '2014-10-20', '20:00', '2014-10-21T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/1/4728.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/1/4728.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Raj test whether they could survive a dark-matter research expedition in a salt mine by simulating the conditions in a steam tunnel. Meanwhile, Leonard and Penny seek advice from Wolowitz and Bernadette after they fight about money.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/13149'),
(14873, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/14873/the-big-bang-theory-8x08-the-prom-equivalency', 'The Prom Equivalency', 8, 8, 'regular', '2014-11-06', '20:00', '2014-11-07T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/3/8064.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/3/8064.jpg', '<p>When the gang recreates a high school prom on the roof the of the guys\' apartment building, Sheldon feels pressure to participate in all the typical romantic traditions.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/14873'),
(31863, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/31863/the-big-bang-theory-8x07-the-misinterpretation-agitation', 'The Misinterpretation Agitation', 8, 7, 'regular', '2014-10-30', '20:00', '2014-10-31T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/2/6683.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/2/6683.jpg', '<p>The guys try to help Penny out of an awkward work dilemma. Meanwhile, Amy and Bernadette argue over whether or not female scientists should play up their sexuality.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/31863'),
(39636, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/39636/the-big-bang-theory-8x09-the-septum-deviation', 'The Septum Deviation', 8, 9, 'regular', '2014-11-13', '20:00', '2014-11-14T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/4/10587.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/10587.jpg', '<p>When Leonard gets minor surgery on his nose, Sheldon is the one in need of sympathy. Meanwhile, Raj\'s parents\' impending divorce causes Howard and Bernadette to work on their own marriage.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/39636'),
(40995, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/40995/the-big-bang-theory-8x10-the-champagne-reflection', 'The Champagne Reflection', 8, 10, 'regular', '2014-11-20', '20:00', '2014-11-21T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/8/21689.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/8/21689.jpg', '<p>Sheldon says a tearful goodbye to \"Fun with Flags.\" Also, Leonard, Howard and Raj look for something significant in a dead professor\'s research, and Bernadette is shocked to learn her co-workers\' true feelings from Penny.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/40995'),
(50184, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/50184/the-big-bang-theory-8x11-the-clean-room-infiltration', 'The Clean Room Infiltration', 8, 11, 'regular', '2014-12-11', '20:00', '2014-12-12T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/5/14957.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/5/14957.jpg', '<p>On Christmas Eve, Amy plans a traditional Victorian dinner, while Raj, Leonard and Howard scramble to remove a pigeon that flew into the clean room at the university. To prove a point to Amy, a Scrooge-like Sheldon buys her the worst possible gift.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/50184'),
(60532, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/60532/the-big-bang-theory-8x12-the-space-probe-disintegration', 'The Space Probe Disintegration', 8, 12, 'regular', '2015-01-08', '20:00', '2015-01-09T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/7/18901.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/7/18901.jpg', '<p>Wolowitz tries to distract Raj, who is anxiously awaiting data from a space probe he helped launch. Meanwhile, Sheldon and Leonard go dress shopping with Penny and Amy.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/60532'),
(93521, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/93521/the-big-bang-theory-8x13-the-anxiety-optimization', 'The Anxiety Optimization', 8, 13, 'regular', '2015-01-29', '20:00', '2015-01-30T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/8/20054.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/8/20054.jpg', '<p>The gang tries to help Sheldon when he becomes stuck in a rut at work by increasing his anxiety level. Howard teases Raj with a new game called \"Cinnamon or Emily?\"</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/93521'),
(124086, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/124086/the-big-bang-theory-8x14-the-troll-manifestation', 'The Troll Manifestation', 8, 14, 'regular', '2015-02-05', '20:00', '2015-02-06T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/8/20814.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/8/20814.jpg', '<p>After Leonard and Sheldon co-publish a physics paper, they must defend themselves against criticism from an online bully. Also, girls\' night finds Penny, Amy and Bernadette confronting embarrassing moments from their past.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/124086'),
(124087, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/124087/the-big-bang-theory-8x15-the-comic-book-store-regeneration', 'The Comic Book Store Regeneration', 8, 15, 'regular', '2015-02-19', '20:00', '2015-02-20T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/8/22003.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/8/22003.jpg', '<p>Wolowitz receives some shocking news as everyone prepares for the reopening of Stuart\'s comic book store. Penny teaches Sheldon how to \"let it go,\" but can\'t follow her own advice after she learns something infuriating about Amy. Also, Leonard and Raj think they spot Nathan Fillion at a restaurant.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/124087'),
(124088, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/124088/the-big-bang-theory-8x16-the-intimacy-acceleration', 'The Intimacy Acceleration', 8, 16, 'regular', '2015-02-26', '20:00', '2015-02-27T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/8/22442.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/8/22442.jpg', '<p>As a joke, Sheldon and Penny try an experiment designed to make participants fall in love. Also, Leonard, Amy, Raj and Emily spend the evening trying to escape a room with a \"zombie.\" And, after returning from Mrs. Wolowitz\' funeral, Bernadette and Howard run into trouble at the airport.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/124088'),
(140767, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/140767/the-big-bang-theory-8x17-the-colonization-application', 'The Colonization Application', 8, 17, 'regular', '2015-03-05', '20:00', '2015-03-06T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/9/23019.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/9/23019.jpg', '<p>Trouble arises when Amy learns Sheldon has applied for a one-way mission to colonize Mars. Also, a trip to the pet store ends in a fight for Sheldon and Amy, Leonard surprises Penny with a very \"adult\" purchase, and, Raj is caught snooping in Emily\'s apartment.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/140767'),
(141514, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/141514/the-big-bang-theory-8x18-the-leftover-thermalization', 'The Leftover Thermalization', 8, 18, 'regular', '2015-03-12', '20:00', '2015-03-13T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/9/23725.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/9/23725.jpg', '<p>Friction ensues when a magazine fails to mention Leonard in an article about the paper he co-wrote with Sheldon. Also, a blackout at Mrs. Wolowitz\'s home leads to a final family dinner in her honor.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/141514'),
(150779, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/150779/the-big-bang-theory-8x19-the-skywalker-incursion', 'The Skywalker Incursion', 8, 19, 'regular', '2015-04-02', '20:00', '2015-04-03T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/9/24939.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/9/24939.jpg', '<p>When Leonard and Sheldon are invited to speak at UC Berkeley, they take a detour to try to meet an idol. Also, when Bernadette and Howard battle over the fate of his Dr. Who TARDIS, Raj and Amy offer to settle the dispute with a game of ping pong.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/150779'),
(150780, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/150780/the-big-bang-theory-8x20-the-fortification-implementation', 'The Fortification Implementation', 8, 20, 'regular', '2015-04-09', '20:00', '2015-04-10T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/10/25283.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/25283.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon and Amy build a blanket fort, they come to major crossroads in their relationship. Also, Wolowitz meets the half-brother he never knew he had, and when Penny is invited to appear on Wil Wheaton\'s podcast, she and Leonard have a huge, on-air argument.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/150780'),
(151474, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/151474/the-big-bang-theory-8x21-the-communication-deterioration', 'The Communication Deterioration', 8, 21, 'regular', '2015-04-16', '20:00', '2015-04-17T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/10/25898.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/25898.jpg', '<p>When Raj is asked to create a message in case a NASA mission discovers alien life, the guys fight over what he should do. Also, Penny is torn between auditioning for a movie or keeping her successful pharmaceutical sales job.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/151474'),
(151475, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/151475/the-big-bang-theory-8x22-the-graduation-transmission', 'The Graduation Transmission', 8, 22, 'regular', '2015-04-23', '20:00', '2015-04-24T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/10/26335.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26335.jpg', '<p>Wolowitz questions his engineering abilities when he and Sheldon can\'t get a toy drone to fly. Meanwhile, a cancelled flight nearly prevents Leonard from giving the commencement address at his former high school, and Raj pits his parents against each other when his father cuts him off financially.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/151475');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `url`, `name`, `season`, `number`, `type`, `airdate`, `airtime`, `airstamp`, `runtime`, `imagemedium`, `imageoriginal`, `summary`, `linksselfhref`) VALUES
(151476, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/151476/the-big-bang-theory-8x23-the-maternal-combustion', 'The Maternal Combustion', 8, 23, 'regular', '2015-04-30', '20:00', '2015-05-01T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/10/26639.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26639.jpg', '<p>Personalities collide when Sheldon and Leonard\'s mothers finally meet. Meanwhile, Howard finally decides to \"man up\" and do his fair share of the housework - but not without a little help from his friends.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/151476'),
(151477, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/151477/the-big-bang-theory-8x24-the-commitment-determination', 'The Commitment Determination', 8, 24, 'regular', '2015-05-07', '20:00', '2015-05-08T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/10/26990.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/10/26990.jpg', '<p>In the Season 8 finale, Leonard and Penny are pressured to set a wedding date by Sheldon, whose relationship with Amy has taken an interesting turn.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/151477'),
(167439, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/167439/the-big-bang-theory-9x01-the-matrimonial-momentum', 'The Matrimonial Momentum', 9, 1, 'regular', '2015-09-21', '20:00', '2015-09-22T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/19/49900.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/19/49900.jpg', '<p>After driving to Vegas to get married, Penny struggles with Leonard\'s confession that he kissed another girl. Also, Sheldon doesn\'t know how to act after Amy pushes pause on their relationship.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/167439'),
(206088, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/206088/the-big-bang-theory-9x02-the-separation-oscillation', 'The Separation Oscillation', 9, 2, 'regular', '2015-09-28', '20:00', '2015-09-29T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/21/54054.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/21/54054.jpg', '<p>Leonard confronts the woman he kissed on the North Sea in an attempt to set Penny\'s mind at ease. Also, Sheldon films a special episode of \"Fun with Flags\" after his breakup with Amy, and Bernadette feels guilty about withholding a secret from Penny.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/206088'),
(208295, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/208295/the-big-bang-theory-9x03-the-bachelor-party-corrosion', 'The Bachelor Party Corrosion', 9, 3, 'regular', '2015-10-05', '20:00', '2015-10-06T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/22/57320.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/22/57320.jpg', '<p>The guys surprise Leonard with a belated bachelor-party weekend in Mexico, but their plans hit a bump in the road when they get a flat tire on the way. Meanwhile, the girls lean on Penny to tell her unsuspecting family that she and Leonard eloped.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/208295'),
(228310, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/228310/the-big-bang-theory-9x04-the-2003-approximation', 'The 2003 Approximation', 9, 4, 'regular', '2015-10-12', '20:00', '2015-10-13T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/24/60466.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/24/60466.jpg', '<p>Sheldon learns of an impending change in his living arrangements and decides to revert back to 2003, a simpler time before he met Leonard and Penny. Also, Howard and Raj form a band to play at the Comic Book Store.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/228310'),
(252299, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/252299/the-big-bang-theory-9x05-the-perspiration-implementation', 'The Perspiration Implementation', 9, 5, 'regular', '2015-10-19', '20:00', '2015-10-20T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/25/63818.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/25/63818.jpg', '<p>The guys take a fencing lesson from Barry Kripke and Sheldon finds himself in an awkward position when Kripke expresses interest in Amy. Also, when Stuart struggles to get female customers at the Comic Book Store, Penny, Amy and Bernadette come by to help him out.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/252299'),
(321678, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/321678/the-big-bang-theory-9x07-the-spock-resonance', 'The Spock Resonance', 9, 7, 'regular', '2015-11-05', '20:00', '2015-11-06T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/28/70784.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/28/70784.jpg', '<p>While being interviewed for a documentary about Spock from \"Star Trek\", Sheldon struggles to suppress his emotions about his recent break-up with Amy. Also, Wolowitz and Bernadette butt heads over remodeling his childhood home.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/321678'),
(353007, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/353007/the-big-bang-theory-9x06-the-helium-insufficiency', 'The Helium Insufficiency', 9, 6, 'regular', '2015-10-26', '20:00', '2015-10-27T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/26/66085.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/26/66085.jpg', '<p>In the midst of a nation-wide helium shortage, Sheldon and Leonard take desperate measures to get the supplies they need. Also, Penny and Bernadette download a dating app on Amy\'s phone to try and find her a new man.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/353007'),
(398404, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/398404/the-big-bang-theory-9x08-the-mystery-date-observation', 'The Mystery Date Observation', 9, 8, 'regular', '2015-11-12', '20:00', '2015-11-13T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/29/74753.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/29/74753.jpg', '<p>When Leonard, Penny and Bernadette learn that Amy is going out on a dinner date, the trio set out to spy on her and the guy. Meanwhile, Sheldon recruits Raj and Howard to find a woman for him, since they were responsible for getting Amy and him together.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/398404'),
(409180, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/409180/the-big-bang-theory-9x09-the-platonic-permutation', 'The Platonic Permutation', 9, 9, 'regular', '2015-11-19', '20:00', '2015-11-20T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/31/77852.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/31/77852.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy try hanging out as friends when they spend Thanksgiving together at the aquarium. Also, Wolowitz reluctantly agrees to volunteer at the soup kitchen with Bernadette, Raj and Emily, and Penny discovers that Leonard knows more about her than she thought.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/409180'),
(466109, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/466109/the-big-bang-theory-9x10-the-earworm-reverberation', 'The Earworm Reverberation', 9, 10, 'regular', '2015-12-10', '20:00', '2015-12-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/35/88078.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/35/88078.jpg', '<p>Sheldon has a revelation when he realizes why a song was stuck in his head. Also, Amy invites Dave over for dinner despite their previously awkward date, and Wolowitz and Koothrappali become obsessed with a fan of their band, \"Footprints on the Moon\".</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/466109'),
(478687, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/478687/the-big-bang-theory-9x11-the-opening-night-excitation', 'The Opening Night Excitation', 9, 11, 'regular', '2015-12-17', '20:00', '2015-12-18T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/35/88073.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/35/88073.jpg', '<p>As the guys prepare to go to the premiere of the new Star Wars movie, Sheldon plans a special event for Amy\'s birthday. Also, Leonard, Wolowitz, and Koothrappali must decide who will take their extra Star Wars movie ticket.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/478687'),
(529350, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/529350/the-big-bang-theory-9x12-the-sales-call-sublimation', 'The Sales Call Sublimation', 9, 12, 'regular', '2016-01-07', '20:00', '2016-01-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/38/95653.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/38/95653.jpg', '<p>Penny gets more than she bargained for when Leonard agrees to meet with a psychiatrist on her behalf. Also, Sheldon and Koothrappali collaborate on an astronomical discovery, and Wolowitz and Bernadette can\'t believe what they are feeling after Stuart moves out.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/529350'),
(536858, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/536858/the-big-bang-theory-9x13-the-empathy-optimization', 'The Empathy Optimization', 9, 13, 'regular', '2016-01-14', '20:00', '2016-01-15T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/39/99008.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/39/99008.jpg', '<p>After having to deal with a sick Sheldon, Leonard, Penny and the gang try to treat themselves to a Sheldon-free weekend.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/536858'),
(569144, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/569144/the-big-bang-theory-9x14-the-meemaw-materialization', 'The Meemaw Materialization', 9, 14, 'regular', '2016-02-04', '20:00', '2016-02-05T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/42/105461.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/42/105461.jpg', '<p>Sheldon\'s thrilled when his Meemaw comes to visit, but his excitement quickly fades when she butts heads with Amy. Also, Raj meets a new girl at the comic book store who makes him question his relationship with Emily.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/569144'),
(579822, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/579822/the-big-bang-theory-9x15-the-valentino-submergence', 'The Valentino Submergence', 9, 15, 'regular', '2016-02-11', '20:00', '2016-02-12T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/43/109341.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/43/109341.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy host a live Valentine\'s Day episode of Fun with Flags, Leonard and Penny grapple with getting older, Howard and Bernadette find a surprise in their hot tub and Raj is torn between Emily and the cute girl he met at the Comic Bookstore.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/579822'),
(599948, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/599948/the-big-bang-theory-9x16-the-positive-negative-reaction', 'The Positive Negative Reaction', 9, 16, 'regular', '2016-02-18', '20:00', '2016-02-19T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/45/112735.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/45/112735.jpg', '<p>When the gang finds out about Bernadette\'s pregnancy, they celebrate by singing karaoke. Also, Bernadette is concerned when Wolowitz freaks out over her pregnancy announcement, and Wolowitz is convinced he must make more money to provide for the baby.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/599948'),
(604630, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/604630/the-big-bang-theory-9x17-the-celebration-experimentation', 'The Celebration Experimentation', 9, 17, 'regular', '2016-02-25', '20:00', '2016-02-26T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/45/114362.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/45/114362.jpg', '<p>After more than nine years together, the gang finally celebrates Sheldon\'s birthday, surprising him with a special guest.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/604630'),
(621664, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/621664/the-big-bang-theory-9x18-the-application-deterioration', 'The Application Deterioration', 9, 18, 'regular', '2016-03-10', '20:00', '2016-03-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/47/118490.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/47/118490.jpg', '<p>Leonard, Sheldon, and Wolowitz run into problems when they file for a patent for their infinite persistence gyroscope. Also, Penny, Amy and Bernadette give Koothrappali dating advice when Emily reaches out to him after their breakup.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/621664'),
(642013, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/642013/the-big-bang-theory-9x19-the-solder-excursion-diversion', 'The Solder Excursion Diversion', 9, 19, 'regular', '2016-03-31', '20:00', '2016-04-01T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/50/126936.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/50/126936.jpg', '<p>Amy is shocked at a revelation from Sheldon after she buys him a new laptop. Also, Koothrappali sells out Leonard and Wolowitz after they lie to their wives in order to attend an early screening of a movie.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/642013'),
(659969, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/659969/the-big-bang-theory-9x20-the-big-bear-precipitation', 'The Big Bear Precipitation', 9, 20, 'regular', '2016-04-07', '20:00', '2016-04-08T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/52/130380.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/52/130380.jpg', '<p>Sheldon spills a secret of Leonard\'s when the two take a weekend cabin trip with Penny and Amy. Also, when Koothrappali goes overboard with pregnancy gifts, Wolowitz and Bernadette must draw the line.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/659969'),
(663422, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663422/the-big-bang-theory-9x21-the-viewing-party-combustion', 'The Viewing Party Combustion', 9, 21, 'regular', '2016-04-21', '20:00', '2016-04-22T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/55/137822.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/55/137822.jpg', '<p>Everyone must choose sides when a small argument between Leonard and Sheldon erupts into a heated fight during a group get-together.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/663422'),
(663423, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663423/the-big-bang-theory-9x22-the-fermentation-bifurcation', 'The Fermentation Bifurcation', 9, 22, 'regular', '2016-04-28', '20:00', '2016-04-29T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/55/137821.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/55/137821.jpg', '<p>The gang goes to a wine bar and runs into Penny\'s old boyfriend, Zack. Also, Bernadette gets stuck spending the evening with Sheldon when she can\'t go wine tasting with the group, and things don\'t go as planned when Koothrappali introduces his new girlfriend, Claire.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/663423'),
(663424, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663424/the-big-bang-theory-9x23-the-line-substitution-solution', 'The Line Substitution Solution', 9, 23, 'regular', '2016-05-05', '20:00', '2016-05-06T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/56/140332.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/56/140332.jpg', '<p>Sheldon hires Stuart to spend the day with Amy when he\'d rather go to a movie screening. Also, Leonard\'s mother, Beverly, comes to town and Penny struggles to make a connection with her.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/663424'),
(663425, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/663425/the-big-bang-theory-9x24-the-convergence-convergence', 'The Convergence Convergence', 9, 24, 'regular', '2016-05-12', '20:00', '2016-05-13T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/55/139271.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/55/139271.jpg', '<p>Chaos ensues when Leonard\'s recently divorced parents, Alfred and Beverly, and Sheldon\'s devoutly religious mother, Mary, come to town. Also, Wolowitz and Koothrappali think the government is out to get them when they are contacted about their guidance system.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/663425'),
(843420, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/843420/the-big-bang-theory-10x01-the-conjugal-conjecture', 'The Conjugal Conjecture', 10, 1, 'regular', '2016-09-19', '20:00', '2016-09-20T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/75/189808.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/75/189808.jpg', '<p>After Sheldon\'s mother and Leonard\'s father share an evening together, everyone deals with an awkward morning the following day. Also, Penny\'s family arrives for the ceremony, including her anxiety-ridden mother, Susan, and her drug dealing brother, Randall.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/843420'),
(844285, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/844285/the-big-bang-theory-10x02-the-military-miniaturization', 'The Military Miniaturization', 10, 2, 'regular', '2016-09-26', '20:00', '2016-09-27T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/75/189160.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/75/189160.jpg', '<p>Colonel Williams, an Air Force representative from the Department of Material Command sits down to talk with Wolowitz.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/844285'),
(844286, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/844286/the-big-bang-theory-10x03-the-dependence-transcendence', 'The Dependence Transcendence', 10, 3, 'regular', '2016-10-03', '20:00', '2016-10-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/78/196809.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/78/196809.jpg', '<p>Tensions rise when the boys struggle to complete their government project on time and Sheldon tries an energy drink to stay awake. Also, Penny and Amy go to a \"party\" at Bert the geologist\'s house, and Kooothrappali learns Bernadette\'s true feelings about her pregnancy when they clean out the future baby room.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/844286'),
(844288, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/844288/the-big-bang-theory-10x04-the-cohabitation-experimentation', 'The Cohabitation Experimentation', 10, 4, 'regular', '2016-10-10', '20:00', '2016-10-11T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/79/198605.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/79/198605.jpg', '<p>When Amy\'s apartment floods, she proposes a \"cohabitation experiment\" with Sheldon. Also, Howard and Bernadette are upset when Koothrappali learns the gender of the baby before they do.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/844288'),
(844292, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/844292/the-big-bang-theory-10x05-the-hot-tub-contamination', 'The Hot Tub Contamination', 10, 5, 'regular', '2016-10-17', '20:00', '2016-10-18T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/80/201958.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/80/201958.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Penny must separate a quarreling Sheldon and Amy when their cohabitation does not go as planned, and Sheldon threatens to break off their relationship when Amy refuses to adhere to the bathroom schedule. Also, Howard and Bernadette find unexpected guests at their house when they decide to stay home from a planned vacation.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/844292'),
(844300, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/844300/the-big-bang-theory-10x06-the-fetal-kick-catalyst', 'The Fetal Kick Catalyst', 10, 6, 'regular', '2016-10-27', '20:00', '2016-10-28T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/82/207208.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/82/207208.jpg', '<p>Penny is surprised to learn she has fans of her performance in \"Serial Ape-ist\" when she attends Van Nuys Comic Con with Leonard. Also, Amy hosts a Sheldon-style brunch at Penny\'s apartment, and Wolowitz makes an impulsive purchase when he starts stressing out about the baby on the way.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/844300'),
(965463, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/965463/the-big-bang-theory-10x07-the-veracity-elasticity', 'The Veracity Elasticity', 10, 7, 'regular', '2016-11-03', '20:00', '2016-11-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/84/210793.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/84/210793.jpg', '<p>In order to continue living with Sheldon, Amy lies to him about repairs being made to her apartment and they host an \"on location\" episode of \"Fun With Flags\" in Penny\'s apartment. Also, Leonard lets Penny decorate Sheldon\'s old room after he learns that she has been secretly moving Leonard\'s collectibles into storage.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/965463'),
(974904, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/974904/the-big-bang-theory-10x08-the-brain-bowl-incubation', 'The Brain Bowl Incubation', 10, 8, 'regular', '2016-11-10', '20:00', '2016-11-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/84/210794.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/84/210794.jpg', '<p>After a successful experiment combining their genes, Sheldon will stop at nothing to convince Amy they should procreate. Also, Koothrappali is embarrassed to tell the gang what the new woman he\'s dating does for a living.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/974904'),
(979245, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/979245/the-big-bang-theory-10x09-the-geology-elevation', 'The Geology Elevation', 10, 9, 'regular', '2016-11-17', '20:00', '2016-11-18T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/213120.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/85/213120.jpg', '<p>When Bert, a Caltech geologist, wins the MacArthur Genius fellowship, Sheldon is overcome with jealousy. Also, Wolowitz finds an old remote control Stephen Hawking action figure he invented.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/979245'),
(991390, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/991390/the-big-bang-theory-10x10-the-property-division-collision', 'The Property Division Collision', 10, 10, 'regular', '2016-12-01', '20:00', '2016-12-02T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/89/223174.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/89/223174.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Leonard must divide up their possessions and remove Penny\'s things from 4B.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/991390'),
(996784, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/996784/the-big-bang-theory-10x11-the-birthday-synchronicity', 'The Birthday Synchronicity', 10, 11, 'regular', '2016-12-15', '20:00', '2016-12-16T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/89/223173.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/89/223173.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy attempt to have an intimate moment together to celebrate Amy\'s birthday; Bernadette and Wolowitz welcome their newborn baby to the world.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/996784'),
(1009072, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1009072/the-big-bang-theory-10x12-the-holiday-summation', 'The Holiday Summation', 10, 12, 'regular', '2017-01-05', '20:00', '2017-01-06T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/92/230610.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/92/230610.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy visit Leonard and Penny for the first time since the holidays and share details about their terrible trip to Texas.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1009072'),
(1015881, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1015881/the-big-bang-theory-10x13-the-romance-recalibration', 'The Romance Recalibration', 10, 13, 'regular', '2017-01-19', '20:00', '2017-01-20T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/94/235969.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/94/235969.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Penny ask for Sheldon\'s and Amy\'s help on putting the romance back in their marriage. Howard and Raj go to extreme lengths to stop the floor in Halley\'s bedroom from making noise.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1015881'),
(1039332, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1039332/the-big-bang-theory-10x14-the-emotion-detection-automation', 'The Emotion Detection Automation', 10, 14, 'regular', '2017-02-02', '20:00', '2017-02-03T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/96/241037.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/96/241037.jpg', '<p>Sheldon beta tests an MIT invention after hearing it can help him read people\'s emotions. Also, Leonard can\'t hide his feelings when Penny announces her brother is coming to town and Raj invites his ex-girlfriends over to give him dating advice.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1039332'),
(1044110, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1044110/the-big-bang-theory-10x15-the-locomotion-reverberation', 'The Locomotion Reverberation', 10, 15, 'regular', '2017-02-09', '20:00', '2017-02-10T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/97/243824.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/97/243824.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Wolowitz try to distract Sheldon when he slows the progress of their guidance system. Also, Penny and Amy take Bernadette out for the night, leaving Raj and Stuart to care for baby Halley.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1044110'),
(1056662, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1056662/the-big-bang-theory-10x16-the-allowance-evaporation', 'The Allowance Evaporation', 10, 16, 'regular', '2017-02-16', '20:00', '2017-02-17T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/98/247215.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/98/247215.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy have their first fight since moving in together, and Koothrappali is shocked at the realities of financial independence when he stops receiving support from his father.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1056662'),
(1067421, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1067421/the-big-bang-theory-10x17-the-comic-con-conundrum', 'The Comic-Con Conundrum', 10, 17, 'regular', '2017-02-23', '20:00', '2017-02-24T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/99/249435.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/99/249435.jpg', '<p>With Koothrappali cut off from his father\'s fortune, he appoints Sheldon to help him get out of debt. Also, Penny considers joining Leonard at Comic-Con.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1067421'),
(1080748, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1080748/the-big-bang-theory-10x18-the-escape-hatch-identification', 'The Escape Hatch Identification', 10, 18, 'regular', '2017-03-09', '20:00', '2017-03-10T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/101/253767.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/101/253767.jpg', '<p>When Raj moves out of his apartment, Leonard and Penny offer him Sheldon\'s old room.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1080748'),
(1095381, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1095381/the-big-bang-theory-10x19-the-collaboration-fluctuation', 'The Collaboration Fluctuation', 10, 19, 'regular', '2017-03-30', '20:00', '2017-03-31T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/104/262432.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/104/262432.jpg', '<p>Leonard, Penny and Raj adjust to their new living arrangement, and Sheldon takes an interest in Amy\'s work.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1095381'),
(1099979, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1099979/the-big-bang-theory-10x20-the-recollection-dissipation', 'The Recollection Dissipation', 10, 20, 'regular', '2017-04-06', '20:00', '2017-04-07T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/105/264736.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/105/264736.jpg', '<p>Sheldon pushes himself to the limit when he collaborates on projects with Leonard and Wolowitz as well as Amy on the same day. Also, Bernadette is nearing the end of her maternity leave and must return to work.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1099979'),
(1107584, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107584/the-big-bang-theory-10x21-the-separation-agitation', 'The Separation Agitation', 10, 21, 'regular', '2017-04-13', '20:00', '2017-04-14T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/108/270249.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/108/270249.jpg', '<p>Howard and Bernadette have a hard time leaving Halley in day care when Bernadette returns to work. Also, Bert introduces the gang to his new girlfriend, Rebecca.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107584'),
(1107585, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107585/the-big-bang-theory-10x22-the-cognition-regeneration', 'The Cognition Regeneration', 10, 22, 'regular', '2017-04-27', '20:00', '2017-04-28T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/109/273806.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/109/273806.jpg', '<p>Leonard isn\'t thrilled when Penny considers taking a new job offered by her ex-boyfriend, Zack.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107585'),
(1107586, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107586/the-big-bang-theory-10x23-the-gyroscopic-collapse', 'The Gyroscopic Collapse', 10, 23, 'regular', '2017-05-04', '20:00', '2017-05-05T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/110/276419.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/110/276419.jpg', '<p>After Leonard, Sheldon and Wolowitz celebrate the completion of the top secret air force project, they are met with an unpleasant surprise. Also, Amy is offered a summer position as a visiting researcher.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107586'),
(1107587, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107587/the-big-bang-theory-10x24-the-long-distance-dissonance', 'The Long Distance Dissonance', 10, 24, 'regular', '2017-05-11', '20:00', '2017-05-12T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/111/278822.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/111/278822.jpg', '<p>The gang is concerned when Sheldon\'s former admirer, Dr. Ramona Nowitzki, resurfaces while Amy is away at Princeton.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1107587'),
(1175046, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1175046/the-big-bang-theory-11x01-the-proposal-proposal', 'The Proposal Proposal', 11, 1, 'regular', '2017-09-25', '20:00', '2017-09-26T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/142/355239.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/142/355239.jpg', '<p>Amy gives Sheldon an answer to his proposal while Howard and Bernadette struggle with some unexpected news.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1175046'),
(1200871, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1200871/the-big-bang-theory-11x02-the-retraction-reaction', 'The Retraction Reaction', 11, 2, 'regular', '2017-10-02', '20:00', '2017-10-03T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/142/355242.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/142/355242.jpg', '<p>Leonard angers the university – and the entire physics community – after he gives an embarrassing interview. Also, Amy and Bernadette bond over having to hide their success from Sheldon and Howard.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1200871'),
(1297342, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1297342/the-big-bang-theory-11x03-the-relaxation-integration', 'The Relaxation Integration', 11, 3, 'regular', '2017-10-09', '20:00', '2017-10-10T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/142/355243.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/142/355243.jpg', '<p>As Sheldon stresses about picking a wedding date, Amy tries to convince him he has a more laid-back side. Also, Koothrappali and Stuart compete to win the heart of Bernadette\'s new coworker, Ruchi.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1297342'),
(1297356, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1297356/the-big-bang-theory-11x04-the-explosion-implosion', 'The Explosion Implosion', 11, 4, 'regular', '2017-10-16', '20:00', '2017-10-17T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/131/329424.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/131/329424.jpg', '<p>Howard and Sheldon bond when they drive to the desert to shoot off a model rocket. Also, when Leonard\'s mom, Beverly, finds a new best friend in Penny, it rubs Leonard the wrong way.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1297356'),
(1312313, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1312313/the-big-bang-theory-11x05-the-collaboration-contamination', 'The Collaboration Contamination', 11, 5, 'regular', '2017-10-23', '20:00', '2017-10-24T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/331050.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/132/331050.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Koothrappali confide in Bernadette when they can\'t handle Amy and Wolowitz working together. Also, Penny and Leonard learn new tactics for how to deal Sheldon from an unlikely source.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1312313'),
(1312314, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1312314/the-big-bang-theory-11x06-the-proton-regeneration', 'The Proton Regeneration', 11, 6, 'regular', '2017-11-02', '20:00', '2017-11-03T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/132/332326.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/132/332326.jpg', '<p>Sheldon goes head-to-head with Wil Wheaton for the role of the new Professor Proton. Also, Penny steps in to take care of Halley when Bernadette and Wolowitz both wind up on bed rest.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1312314'),
(1312315, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1312315/the-big-bang-theory-11x07-the-geology-methodology', 'The Geology Methodology', 11, 7, 'regular', '2017-11-09', '20:00', '2017-11-10T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/134/335924.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/134/335924.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Bert collaborate on a research project, despite Sheldon\'s embarrassment. Also, Penny and Bernadette coach Koothrappali on how to navigate his relationship with Ruchi.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1312315'),
(1335922, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1335922/the-big-bang-theory-11x08-the-tesla-recoil', 'The Tesla Recoil', 11, 8, 'regular', '2017-11-16', '20:00', '2017-11-17T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/135/339330.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/135/339330.jpg', '<p>Leonard and Wolowitz are furious after they learn Sheldon went to work with the military behind their backs. Also, while Bernadette is on bed rest, she asks Raj to do some digging when she suspects Ruchi is trying to steal her job.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1335922'),
(1347686, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1347686/the-big-bang-theory-11x09-the-bitcoin-entanglement', 'The Bitcoin Entanglement', 11, 9, 'regular', '2017-11-30', '20:00', '2017-12-01T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/136/342276.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/136/342276.jpg', '<p>Sheldon tries to teach the guys a lesson after they cut him out of a potentially valuable Bitcoin investment. Also, a seven-year-old video reveals a secret about Leonard and Penny\'s relationship.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1347686'),
(1356367, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1356367/the-big-bang-theory-11x10-the-confidence-erosion', 'The Confidence Erosion', 11, 10, 'regular', '2017-12-07', '20:00', '2017-12-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/137/344140.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/137/344140.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy try to eliminate stress from wedding planning by applying math to the process. Also, Koothrappali \"breaks up\" with Wolowitz after realizing his best friend is actually hurting his confidence.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1356367'),
(1360390, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1360390/the-big-bang-theory-11x11-the-celebration-reverberation', 'The Celebration Reverberation', 11, 11, 'regular', '2017-12-14', '20:00', '2017-12-15T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/138/346472.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/138/346472.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Wolowitz plan birthday celebrations for Amy and Halley, respectively. Also, Leonard receives a Christmas letter from his brother that causes him to spiral out about his own lack of accomplishments.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1360390'),
(1364184, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1364184/the-big-bang-theory-11x12-the-matrimonial-metric', 'The Matrimonial Metric', 11, 12, 'regular', '2018-01-04', '20:00', '2018-01-05T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/141/352926.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/141/352926.jpg', '<p>To discover who would be most qualified to be best man and maid of honor at their wedding, Sheldon and Amy subject their friends to a series of secret experiments. Also, Penny reveals her true feelings about Amy.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1364184'),
(1373673, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1373673/the-big-bang-theory-11x13-the-solo-oscillation', 'The Solo Oscillation', 11, 13, 'regular', '2018-01-11', '20:00', '2018-01-12T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/142/355438.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/142/355438.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon kicks Amy out to work solo, she and Leonard bond during a series of science experiments. Also, Bert the geologist replaces Wolowitz in the band Footprints on the Moon, and Sheldon finds Penny a surprising source of scientific inspiration.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1373673'),
(1384413, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1384413/the-big-bang-theory-11x14-the-separation-triangulation', 'The Separation Triangulation', 11, 14, 'regular', '2018-01-18', '20:00', '2018-01-19T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/142/356979.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/142/356979.jpg', '<p>Koothrappali finds himself in the middle of domestic drama when he learns the woman he\'s dating, Nell, has a very upset husband, Oliver. Also, when Sheldon rents his old room back for a quiet place to work, he drives Leonard crazy by being a model tenant.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1384413'),
(1391498, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1391498/the-big-bang-theory-11x15-the-novelization-correlation', 'The Novelization Correlation', 11, 15, 'regular', '2018-02-01', '20:00', '2018-02-02T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/144/361596.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/144/361596.jpg', '<p> When Sheldon petitions Wil Wheaton to appear on the new Professor Proton show, Wil offers a role to Amy instead. Also, Penny gets angry when she thinks the female protagonist in Leonard\'s novel is based on her.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1391498'),
(1402098, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1402098/the-big-bang-theory-11x16-the-neonatal-nomenclature', 'The Neonatal Nomenclature', 11, 16, 'regular', '2018-03-01', '20:00', '2018-03-02T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/147/368495.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/147/368495.jpg', '<p>When Bernadette won\'t go into labor, all her friends try different tactics to get things started. Also, Wolowitz confronts Bernadette after Amy accidentally reveals she\'s already chosen their son\'s name.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1402098'),
(1410334, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1410334/the-big-bang-theory-11x17-the-athenaeum-allocation', 'The Athenaeum Allocation', 11, 17, 'regular', '2018-03-08', '20:00', '2018-03-09T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/148/371530.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/148/371530.jpg', '<p>Leonard jumps through hoops to help secure the perfect wedding venue for Sheldon and Amy. Also, Bernadette and Wolowitz have a hard time deciding who should stay at home with the kids and who should go back to work.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1410334'),
(1415703, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1415703/the-big-bang-theory-11x18-the-gates-excitation', 'The Gates Excitation', 11, 18, 'regular', '2018-03-29', '20:00', '2018-03-30T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/151/379315.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/151/379315.jpg', '<p>Penny gets the opportunity to host Bill Gates at work when his company wants to partner with her pharmaceutical company. Also, Leonard, Koothrappali and Wolowitz do everything in their power to meet him, while Sheldon thinks he is the victim of an April Fools prank.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1415703'),
(1422209, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1422209/the-big-bang-theory-11x19-the-tenant-disassociation', 'The Tenant Disassociation', 11, 19, 'regular', '2018-04-05', '20:00', '2018-04-06T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/151/379314.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/151/379314.jpg', '<p>When Leonard learns Sheldon is the president of the tenants association, he decides to run against him. Also, Bernadette encourages Wolowitz and Koothrappali to find the owner of a drone after they find it in the backyard.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1422209'),
(1425901, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1425901/the-big-bang-theory-11x20-the-reclusive-potential', 'The Reclusive Potential', 11, 20, 'regular', '2018-04-12', '20:00', '2018-04-13T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/152/381194.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/152/381194.jpg', '<p>A brilliant but reclusive scientist, Doctor Wolcott, invites Sheldon to his cabin in the middle of nowhere, and Leonard, Raj and Howard go along for the trip. Also, Penny and Bernadette improvise after Amy doesn\'t like the tame bachelorette party they planned for her.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1425901'),
(1431752, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431752/the-big-bang-theory-11x21-the-comet-polarization', 'The Comet Polarization', 11, 21, 'regular', '2018-04-19', '20:00', '2018-04-20T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/153/382793.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/153/382793.jpg', '<p>Sheldon\'s comic book store experiences changes when writer Neil Gaiman puts Stuart\'s store on the map. Also, Koothrappali takes credit for Penny\'s astronomical discovery, and friendships are threatened.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431752'),
(1431753, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431753/the-big-bang-theory-11x22-the-monetary-insufficiency', 'The Monetary Insufficiency', 11, 22, 'regular', '2018-04-26', '20:00', '2018-04-27T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/154/386157.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/154/386157.jpg', '<p>Sheldon goes to Vegas to win money for science. Also, Penny and Bernadette take Amy wedding dress shopping, but her terrible choice entangles them in a web of lies.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431753'),
(1431754, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431754/the-big-bang-theory-11x23-the-sibling-realignment', 'The Sibling Realignment', 11, 23, 'regular', '2018-05-03', '20:00', '2018-05-04T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/154/386385.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/154/386385.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon learns that his mother won\'t attend his wedding unless he invites his brother, Georgie, he and Leonard travel to Texas to end a family feud. Also, the Wolowitz kids inadvertently infest Amy, Bernadette, Wolowitz and Koothrappali with pinkeye.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431754'),
(1431755, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431755/the-big-bang-theory-11x24-the-bow-tie-asymmetry', 'The Bow Tie Asymmetry', 11, 24, 'regular', '2018-05-10', '20:00', '2018-05-11T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/155/388166.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/155/388166.jpg', '<p>Amy and Sheldon\'s wedding provides Sheldon with the information he needs to make a breakthrough in his symmetrical string theory. Meanwhile, their friends pick up Sheldon and Amy\'s families from the airport, and Mark Hamill agrees to officiate at the ceremony.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1431755'),
(1473815, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1473815/the-big-bang-theory-12x01-the-conjugal-configuration', 'The Conjugal Configuration', 12, 1, 'regular', '2018-09-24', '20:00', '2018-09-25T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/170/425575.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/170/425575.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy\'s honeymoon runs aground in New York, while Penny and Leonard discover they are uncomfortably similar to Amy\'s parents, Mr. and Mrs. Fowler. Also, Koothrappali insults physicist Neil deGrasse Tyson and starts a Twitter war.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1473815'),
(1494024, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1494024/the-big-bang-theory-12x02-the-wedding-gift-wormhole', 'The Wedding Gift Wormhole', 12, 2, 'regular', '2018-09-27', '20:00', '2018-09-28T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/170/425574.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/170/425574.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy drive themselves crazy trying to figure out what \"perfect gift\" Leonard and Penny gave them for their wedding. Also, Koothrappali decides he wants to settle down and asks his father to arrange a marriage for him.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1494024'),
(1533534, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1533534/the-big-bang-theory-12x04-the-tam-turbulence', 'The Tam Turbulence', 12, 4, 'regular', '2018-10-11', '20:00', '2018-10-12T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/171/428314.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/171/428314.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon won\'t tell anyone why he\'s never mentioned Tam, his childhood best friend, Leonard takes matters into his own hands. Also, Bernadette and Penny take out Raj\'s fiancée, Anu, for dinner to get the skinny on her.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1533534'),
(1533789, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1533789/the-big-bang-theory-12x03-the-procreation-calculation', 'The Procreation Calculation', 12, 3, 'regular', '2018-10-04', '20:00', '2018-10-05T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/170/425573.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/170/425573.jpg', '<p>The Wolowitzes\' life gets complicated when Stuart starts bringing his new girlfriend home. Also, Penny and Leonard talk about starting a family while Koothrappali explores an arranged marriage.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1533789'),
(1537478, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1537478/the-big-bang-theory-12x05-the-planetarium-collision', 'The Planetarium Collision', 12, 5, 'regular', '2018-10-18', '20:00', '2018-10-19T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/171/429994.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/171/429994.jpg', '<p>When Amy doesn\'t have time to work on super-asymmetry, Sheldon goes to great lengths to ensure she\'s available to work with him even it if means accidentally sabotaging her career in the process. Also, Koothrappali doesn\'t want Wolowitz to join him in hosting a show at the planetarium.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1537478'),
(1545002, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1545002/the-big-bang-theory-12x06-the-imitation-perturbation', 'The Imitation Perturbation', 12, 6, 'regular', '2018-10-25', '20:00', '2018-10-26T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/172/431129.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/172/431129.jpg', '<p>When Wolowitz dresses up as Sheldon for Halloween, Sheldon seeks retaliation at Leonard and Penny\'s Halloween party. Also, Leonard is shocked that Penny doesn\'t remember their first kiss.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1545002');
INSERT INTO `episodes` (`id`, `url`, `name`, `season`, `number`, `type`, `airdate`, `airtime`, `airstamp`, `runtime`, `imagemedium`, `imageoriginal`, `summary`, `linksselfhref`) VALUES
(1551637, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1551637/the-big-bang-theory-12x07-the-grant-allocation-derivation', 'The Grant Allocation Derivation', 12, 7, 'regular', '2018-11-01', '20:00', '2018-11-02T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/173/433874.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/173/433874.jpg', '<p>Leonard is caught between a rock and a hard place when he\'s responsible for distributing extra grant money. Also, Bernadette turns the backyard playhouse into a hideaway from her husband and kids.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1551637'),
(1556918, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1556918/the-big-bang-theory-12x08-the-consummation-deviation', 'The Consummation Deviation', 12, 8, 'regular', '2018-11-08', '20:00', '2018-11-09T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/174/435544.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/174/435544.jpg', '<p>Sheldon tries to bond with Amy\'s father, but when Wolowitz lures Mr. Fowler away with magic tricks, Sheldon has no choice but to bond with Mrs. Fowler. Also, Koothrappali and Anu try to get physical for the first time.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1556918'),
(1561862, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1561862/the-big-bang-theory-12x09-the-citation-negation', 'The Citation Negation', 12, 9, 'regular', '2018-11-15', '20:00', '2018-11-16T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/174/435847.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/174/435847.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy are devastated after learning from a Russian paper that Super Asymmetry has already been discovered and disproven. Also, ultra-competitive Bernadette asks Stuart\'s girlfriend, Denise, to teach her how to beat Howard in a popular videogame.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1561862'),
(1568746, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1568746/the-big-bang-theory-12x10-the-vcr-illumination', 'The VCR Illumination', 12, 10, 'regular', '2018-12-06', '20:00', '2018-12-07T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/176/441718.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/176/441718.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy are still down about their theory being disproven, but a VHS tape from Sheldon\'s past inspires him not to give up. Also, Bernadette turns into a pageant mom when she tries to help Wolowitz ace his Magic Castle audition.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1568746'),
(1572550, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1572550/the-big-bang-theory-12x11-the-paintball-scattering', 'The Paintball Scattering', 12, 11, 'regular', '2019-01-03', '20:00', '2019-01-04T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/179/447871.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/179/447871.jpg', '<p>Penny and Leonard organize a paintball game that results in mayhem when Sheldon is jealous of Amy. Also, Koothrappali catches Anu with her ex-boyfriend, and Stuart doesn\'t want to move in with Denise.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1572550'),
(1577741, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1577741/the-big-bang-theory-12x12-the-propagation-proposition', 'The Propagation Proposition', 12, 12, 'regular', '2019-01-10', '20:00', '2019-01-11T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/179/449443.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/179/449443.jpg', '<p>Penny\'s ex-boyfriend, Zack, and his wife want a baby, but when Zack is infertile, they ask Leonard for help. Also, Koothrappali attempts to mend things with his ex-fiancée, Anu.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1577741'),
(1587723, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1587723/the-big-bang-theory-12x13-the-confirmation-polarization', 'The Confirmation Polarization', 12, 13, 'regular', '2019-01-17', '20:00', '2019-01-18T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/180/450967.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/180/450967.jpg', '<p>When Sheldon and Amy\'s super asymmetry theory is proven by two physicists, Dr. Pemberton and Dr. Campbell from Chicago, they\'re thrilled, until they try to kick Amy off the Nobel nomination. Also, Bernadette has a big success at work and Penny\'s going to be a part of it – whether she wants to or not.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1587723'),
(1593246, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1593246/the-big-bang-theory-12x14-the-meteorite-manifestation', 'The Meteorite Manifestation', 12, 14, 'regular', '2019-01-31', '20:00', '2019-02-01T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/182/455458.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/182/455458.jpg', '<p>Sheldon is thrilled to help Bernadette and Wolowitz navigate bureaucratic paperwork, until he discovers they are breaking the law. Also, Leonard is disappointed when his friends exclude him from a scientific project.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1593246'),
(1596753, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1596753/the-big-bang-theory-12x15-the-donation-oscillation', 'The Donation Oscillation', 12, 15, 'regular', '2019-02-07', '20:00', '2019-02-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/182/457473.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/182/457473.jpg', '<p>Penny tries to seduce an abstaining Leonard to ruin his \"donation\" for her ex-boyfriend, Zack, and his wife, Marissa. Also, Wolowitz, Bernadette, Anu and Koothrappali turn Koothrappali\'s canceled bachelor party into a couple\'s trip aboard the \"vomit comet\".</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1596753'),
(1600576, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1600576/the-big-bang-theory-12x16-the-d-d-vortex', 'The D & D Vortex', 12, 16, 'regular', '2019-02-21', '20:00', '2019-02-22T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/184/462416.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/184/462416.jpg', '<p>When the gang finds out Wil Wheaton hosts a celebrity Dungeons and Dragons game involving William Shatner, Joe Manganiello, Kareem Abdul-Jabbar and Kevin Smith, deception and betrayal are the path to make it to the one open seat.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1600576'),
(1606257, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1606257/the-big-bang-theory-12x17-the-conference-valuation', 'The Conference Valuation', 12, 17, 'regular', '2019-03-07', '20:00', '2019-03-08T01:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/186/467456.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/186/467456.jpg', '<p>When Penny and Bernadette go to San Diego for a pharmaceutical sales convention, Wolowitz is in charge of the kids. Also, Sheldon finds a book on experimenting on kids, and the guys plus Amy make a day of it.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1606257'),
(1619779, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1619779/the-big-bang-theory-12x18-the-laureate-accumulation', 'The Laureate Accumulation', 12, 18, 'regular', '2019-04-04', '20:00', '2019-04-05T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/190/476575.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/190/476575.jpg', '<p>When competitors Pemberton and Campbell charm America on a publicity tour, Sheldon and Amy try to bring Nobel laureates Kip Thorne, George Smoot and Frances Arnold to their side. Also, Halley\'s fear of the dark leads to opportunity and conflict for Howard, Bernadette and Stuart.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1619779'),
(1628575, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628575/the-big-bang-theory-12x19-the-inspiration-deprivation', 'The Inspiration Deprivation', 12, 19, 'regular', '2019-04-18', '20:00', '2019-04-19T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/192/480675.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/192/480675.jpg', '<p>The concept of what it would mean for women everywhere if Amy were to win a Nobel Prize causes Amy to have a meltdown. Also, Koothrappali and Wolowitz try to relive the good old days after Wolowitz buys a scooter that looks like the one he had years ago.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628575'),
(1628576, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628576/the-big-bang-theory-12x20-the-decision-reverberation', 'The Decision Reverberation', 12, 20, 'regular', '2019-04-25', '20:00', '2019-04-26T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/193/483551.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/193/483551.jpg', '<p>Koothrappali is worried people won\'t take him seriously in his own field after publishing a paper that suggests he may have discovered alien life. Also, Leonard wants to be the principal investigator on a plasma physics study.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628576'),
(1628577, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628577/the-big-bang-theory-12x21-the-plagiarism-schism', 'The Plagiarism Schism', 12, 21, 'regular', '2019-05-02', '20:00', '2019-05-03T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/194/485926.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/194/485926.jpg', '<p>Kripke has proof that Dr. Pemberton plagiarized his thesis in college, and Sheldon and Amy aren\'t sure if they should turn him in or not. Also, Wolowitz is happily surprised to learn that Bernadette wasn\'t the only waitress at the Cheesecake Factory who had a crush on him back in the day.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628577'),
(1628578, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628578/the-big-bang-theory-12x22-the-maternal-conclusion', 'The Maternal Conclusion', 12, 22, 'regular', '2019-05-09', '20:00', '2019-05-10T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/195/489825.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/195/489825.jpg', '<p>Leonard is pleasantly surprised when Beverly comes to visit and she\'s genuinely kind to him, until he finds out the real reason she\'s there. Also, Denise and Stuart overstay their welcome at the Wolowitz house.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628578'),
(1628579, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628579/the-big-bang-theory-12x23-the-change-constant', 'The Change Constant', 12, 23, 'regular', '2019-05-16', '20:00', '2019-05-17T00:00:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/197/493238.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/197/493238.jpg', '<p>Sheldon and Amy await big news.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1628579'),
(1646220, 'http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1646220/the-big-bang-theory-12x24-the-stockholm-syndrome', 'The Stockholm Syndrome', 12, 24, 'regular', '2019-05-16', '20:30', '2019-05-17T00:30:00+00:00', 30, 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/197/493243.jpg', 'http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/197/493243.jpg', '<p>Bernadette and Wolowitz leave their kids for the first time; Penny and Leonard try to keep a secret; Sheldon and Amy stick together; and Koothrappali makes a new friend, as the gang travels together into an uncharted future.</p>', 'http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1646220');
